name: Fundle!
description:
A bundle of fun? A fundle of bun? No, I probably shouldn't use that last one. Let's try again.

Its Fun! Its a Bundle of it! And thus, the Fundle was born!

The Mini Fundle includes a 3" Round "Chumblenuts" Sticker and a custom digital sketch of your choosing by Writer/Artist/Acrobat* Ethan Kocak! And on this item shipping is FREE!

The Giant Fundle includes a Sticker - that same Chumblenuts design as before - a book with a sweet, sweet sketch by our own Writer/Artist/Hot Dog Eating Champion** Ethan Kocak - and a digital sketch emailed to you!

And lastly, the <strike>Mecha</strike>Mega Fundle! It Includes a Sticker, a Shirt, a Book - signed and sketched upon by our very own Writer/Artist/HVAC Technician*** Ethan Kocak, and a digital sketch emailed directly to you!

And whilst it should go without saying... this is for one sticker, one book, and one shirt... and none of the action figures behind them in this photo.

* In this case we mean a user of Adobe Acrobat software.
** This may be an exaggeration. or a complete fabrication.
*** What can I say? He's a multi-talented kind of guy.

name: Stickers
description:
There are 3 different options available:

- 3" Round "Chumblenuts" Sticker: A STICKER! That is THREE INCHES and ROUND! With text saying "CHUMBLENUTS". Also, a fearless image of the Black Mudpuppy who as of this writing has no fear.
- Diecut Black Mudpuppy: A sticker, design of the black mudpuppy himself, diecut and everything!
- Diecut Hitlersaurus: Hitlersaurus in front of a podium, clearly saying something epic.

name: Real Physical Print Books
description: Volume 1 or "Things You Can Read On The Internet For Free": Includes The Obligatory Origin Story, The Invisible Deafmute and Hitlersaurus! Volume 2 "The Dead Trees Edition": Includes: Dr. Hypochondria, Psychopomp & Circumstance and Hel Hath No Fury.

name: Mudpuppy T-Shirt
description: This lovely upper torso cover is in an approximate "T" shape, with a Mudpuppy heavy design in the center. Assorted colors and sizes!
